<section class="global-service-section">
    <div class="content-container">
        <div class="header-block">
            <span class="section-badge">Salud sin Límites</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">
                Acompañamiento Global en<br />Biomagnetismo
            </h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">
                Brindamos salud y bienestar a personas en España, Latinoamérica
                y cualquier rincón del mundo donde se busque el equilibrio.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="explanation-grid">
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="card-icon">
                    <svg
                        aria-hidden="true"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        class="icon-svg"
                    >
                        <path
                            d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Precisión a Distancia</h3>
                <p class="card-text">
                    La energía no entiende de fronteras. Realizamos el rastreo
                    con una efectividad total, conectando con tu bienestar sin
                    importar donde te encuentres en este momento.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="card-icon">
                    <svg
                        aria-hidden="true"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        class="icon-svg"
                    >
                        <circle
                            cx="12"
                            cy="12"
                            r="10"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="1.5"></circle>
                        <path
                            d="M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                        <path
                            d="M2 12h20"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Escucha Natural</h3>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Cada sesión es un diálogo con tu organismo. Identificamos
                    los puntos que necesitan equilibrio para que tu cuerpo
                    recupere su capacidad natural de sanar.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Tarjeta 3: El Resultado -->
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="card-icon">
                    <svg
                        aria-hidden="true"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        class="icon-svg"
                    >
                        <path
                            d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                        <path
                            d="M22 4L12 14.01l-3-3"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Resultados Tangibles</h3>
                <p class="card-text">
                    El equilibrio del terreno biológico surte efecto en tu salud
                    física. Notarás la mejoría en tu bienestar general de manera
                    tan real como si estuviéramos juntos.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="map-overlay"></div>
</section>

<style>
    .global-service-section {
        position: relative;
        padding: 6rem 1rem;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #0f1f1a 0%, #1a1510 100%);
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .content-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 4rem;
    }

    .header-block {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #4ade80;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
        background: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.1);
        border-radius: 2rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.2);
    }

    .section-title {
        font-family: "Playfair Display", Georgia, serif;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
        color: #d4a853;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .section-subtitle {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        line-height: 1.6;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .explanation-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .service-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 1rem;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        transition:
            transform 0.3s ease,
            border-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .service-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        border-color: rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.3);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }

    .card-icon {
        width: 48px;
        height: 48px;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: #d4a853;
    }

    .icon-svg {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .card-title {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-family: "Outfit", sans-serif;
    }

    .card-text {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .map-overlay {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image: radial-gradient(
            circle at 50% 50%,
            rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.05) 1px,
            transparent 1px
        );
        background-size: 40px 40px;
        z-index: 1;
        mask-image: linear-gradient(
            to bottom,
            transparent,
            black 40%,
            black 60%,
            transparent
        );
        opacity: 0.5;
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .explanation-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .global-service-section {
            padding: 4rem 1rem;
        }
    }
</style>
